  "id": "RAW_461d6167",
  "title": "今日开源（2026-3-10）：OpenClaw v2026 正式发布，多平台能力与跨端稳定性同步优化",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247501769&idx=1&sn=9e3233ee8264988d9049c9a6dd9e50c4",
  "date": "2026-03-10 10:30:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：InternAgent 1.5</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"398\" data-imgfileid=\"100018108\" data-ratio=\"0.2490740740740741\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b037058c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFbrFNym2lvJMlmPj8J0LD6ERaB4Ev8m675Q07hqdc13DJZeZiaWPGrolm4LjTJM9WFPLXQf3zhPK9wuibA2XNulyz1YdIS3mF3FY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★InternAgent 1.5是一个统一的自主系统，支持从算法发现到经验发现的端到端科学发现。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">基于InternAgent 1.0，系统将科学探究组织为三个协调的子系统：生成（通过深度研究进行假设构建）、验证（通过解决方案优化进行方法评估）和进化（通过长期记忆进行证据驱动的优化）。InternAgent 1.5在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">科学推理基准测试</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">中表现领先，并在物理、生物、地球和生命科学领域支持算法和经验发现工作流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/internagent\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/internagent</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Muddit</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.649074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"1038\" data-imgfileid=\"100018110\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bcc321ad&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFbg5eAYPvlic5fO4IoNq48K1u0g1R7Qur6bVEtVL5ydCWvOxqESeP7pZBE5kV5pPaKyJ8n5QfFOAibBqoLf803xoRVbn0StaabZk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Muddit是Meissonic家族的下一代基础模型，基于离散扩散技术，实现统一且高效的多模态生成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与传统的自回归方法不同，Muddit利用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">MaskGIT风格的掩码</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">作为核心机制，实现跨模态的快速并行解码。Muddit从视觉优先的角度开发，旨在通过单一架构和解码范式处理多种任务，如文本生成、图像生成和视觉语言推理。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/muddit\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/muddit</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：ThinkMorph</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8111111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"1298\" data-imgfileid=\"100018109\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=89d7da4e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFYSAtEAXTOz8Q4T4c4HAzU0pK9tmkWDib6xfUlYAckaUShPmN4tpzWVpjTGCseRIu1jH5Qeic7qAWqyvE9BU0foYFZhyicL0Vk1Y4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ThinkMorph是一个统一的多模态推理模型，经过约24K高质量交错推理轨迹的微调，能够生成逐步的文本-图像推理步骤，具体操作视觉内容同时保持连贯的语言逻辑。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型在视觉基准测试中表现出色，并具有强大的域外泛化能力，展示了新颖的视觉操作技能和多模态智能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/thinkmorph\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/thinkmorph</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④项目：Sarvam</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3148148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"503\" data-imgfileid=\"100018107\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0ec569fc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFac83voIqCvDO8AOFZBh78trkV4LhniaEQpUD25dr0bn3V8JzBA8g407Dp8dphsQBBt9pdq4MpicBPUaFRicibBp7fCWQEo5sB4BMs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Sarvam是一个先进的Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) 模型，拥有2.4B非嵌入活动参数，主要用于实际部署。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型结合了强大的推理能力、可靠的编码能力和一流的对话质量，特别是在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">印度语言环境</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">中表现出色。Sarvam-旨在在资源受限的环境中可靠运行，能够处理多语言语音通话并执行工具调用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/sarvam\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/sarvam</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：OpenClaw v2026.3.8</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5722222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"916\" data-imgfileid=\"100018112\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0e5c8e41&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFbk4sV4uRqkibf53o83kZbC90dluZzibGPGD4OSia1x5r6UVOHvyCNicy7QicK7U08ZQ1k49zaJkwKpMuruLbhRic4KzI2XpDP34aEMk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★OpenClaw v2026.3.8正式发布，该版本围绕CLI工具链增强、多平台功能迭代、大模型适配升级、工具生态拓展、跨端稳定性修复及安全机制加固完成全方位更新，进一步提升了平台的工程化部署能力、场景适配性与运行可靠性，同时新增多项实用配置，优化了多端使用体验。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">本次更新新增本地备份创建与验证、可配置语音静音超时发送等核心功能，完美适配GPT-5.4大模型的超大上下文窗口，升级Brave网页搜索的LLM上下文能力并标准化搜索提供商排序，修复了Telegram / 飞书 / Matrix等多渠道交互的路由与推送问题，还强化了SSRF防护、脚本执行权限控制等安全机制，并对Podman/Docker等部署环境完成兼容性与权限优化，同时完善了WSL2+Windows跨环境的浏览器调试适配能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/openclaw\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/openclaw</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：AgentHub</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3296296296296296\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"528\" data-imgfileid=\"100018111\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0218d148&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFb2ZVdmKEYL7W7H28F6bl4f3yOz96jch1QecTBBoeI674AW8MhTTJjIPfmibTPncOMTsPw0fcVHKA5hcBVckgibDjiaG1gBkcOB2U%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AgentHub是一个面向Agent的协作平台，旨在为AI Agent提供一个共同工作的环境。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它类似于一个简化版的GitHub，没有主分支、PR或合并，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">只有一个广泛的提交DAG和一个用于Agent协调的消息板。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该平台的第一个应用场景是为之前的项目Autoresearch提供组织层，模拟一个研究社区以实现自主Agent的学术研究。AgentHub的基本概念更为通用，可以用于组织Agent社区以协作完成其他项目。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/agenthub\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/agenthub</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 3 月初发布的多个前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖科学发现自主系统、多模态基础模型、MoE 模型及 Agent 协作平台。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 3 月初发布的多个前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖科学发现自主系统、多模态基础模型、MoE 模型及 Agent 协作平台。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了六项最新的开源 AI 技术进展。在基座模型方面，InternAgent 1.5 提出了统一的科学发现自主系统；Muddit 作为下一代基础模型，利用离散扩散技术实现高效多模态生成；ThinkMorph 专注于高质量交错推理轨迹的微调；Sarvam 则针对印度语言环境优化了 MoE 模型。在工具与平台方面，OpenClaw v2026.3.8 完成了全方位更新，支持 GPT-5.4 并强化了安全机制；AgentHub 则为 AI Agent 提供了一个类似 GitHub 的协作环境，旨在模拟研究社区实现自主学术研究。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "InternAgent 1.5 构建了闭环的科学发现子系统。",
      "explanation": "通过生成（假设构建）、验证（方法评估）和进化（证据驱动优化）三个协调的子系统，支持从算法发现到经验发现的端到端流程。"
    },
